title: Did Elon Musk inform Cany West: " We may have more differences of opinion than I expected? '
subtitle: A person's endorsement of the presidency without knowing the platform to which they would be running is generally a bad idea.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: Elon Musk tweeted, "Maybe we have more differences of opinion than I expected" when he presented an article on the 2020 Canyon West presidential program.
